&gt;    3)	Look for MX(foo.bar.edu), MX(bar.edu) etc. until I get a
&gt;	positive reply or reach the top domain (.edu).

Not a great idea. A host that knows how to reach bar.edu may not necessarily
know how to reach foo.bar.edu. bar.edu may not be able to reach foo.bar.edu,
either. It is best to make no assumptions.

